data.description: Beautiful waterfront home with over 120 feet of waterfront offering expansive views on a large .46 acre lot*Nice dock with boathouse  and 10,000 lb. boatlift with new motor (2022)*Recently updated kitchen features white cabinetry with overhead and under cabinet lighting, Silestone countertop, custom backsplash, stainless appliances , Solar Tube for additional light and engineered vinyl flooring*Large family room features hardwood floors and wood burning fireplace*Main level also features 2 huge bedrooms including large master suite with master bath, separate dining area and sunroom off kitchen leads to nice screened in porch*Finished lower level offers 3rd bedroom, 3rd full bath, laundry room area, storage and access to the garage*Huge lot with room for expansion if you want*Other recent updates include HVAC (2023), updated kitchen (2021), Solar tube in kitchen (2021), new flooring in kitchen and sunroom (2021), Encapsulated crawl space with dehumidifier (2022), new shed (2020),  and Backup electrical hookup for generator (2022).
